                .calculator__calculator-total
                  div 
                    .dropdown-info   
                      | Международная экспресс-доставка
                      span ?
                        .dropdown-info__hidden-text  Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Nulla quas eveniet unde esse, illum alias sint repudiandae quidem beatae nemo.
                  .calculator__total-delivery.calculator__total-wrap
                    .calculator__total-sum
                    span $

                .calculator__calculator-total
                  div 
                    .dropdown-info К оплате
                      
                  .calculator__total-to-pay.calculator__total-wrap
